Hello, thank you for calling West Barnstable Horse Hides, your favorite bowling alley. My name is Alex. How can I assist you today?

Hi Alex, I'm having some questions about my recent billing statement.

I'd be happy to help you with that. May I have your name, please?

Sure, my name is Jamie Smith.

Thank you, Jamie. Can I have your billing account number to pull up your details?

Of course, it's two three four five six seven eight.

Got it, thank you. To verify your identity, could you please confirm the last four digits of your registered phone number?

Yes, the last four digits are five six seven eight.

Thank you, Jamie. I've accessed your account. Your billing issue has been reviewed, and it appears there's an unexpected charge for last week, which I'll address and correct immediately.

Thank you so much, Alex. I appreciate your help!

You're welcome, Jamie. Thank you for your patience. Is there anything else I can assist you with?

No, that would be all. Thanks again!

Alright, thank you for calling West Barnstable Horse Hides. Have a great day!
